                                    Shortcuts
                                    ~~~~~~~~~
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------
        F1   Shows the manual.
    shift    F1   Opens the FileInfo window.
    control  F1   Runs the interactive help.

        F3   Opens the SaveAs window.
    shift    F3   Save the file using the same path as last time.

        F4   Opens the Search window.
    shift    F4   Repeats the previous search.

    control  N    Opens the 'Add Movie' window.
    control  E    Opens the 'Edit Movie' window.
    control  X    Deletes the selected movie.
    control  S    Sorts the list.

    control  A    Selects all movies in the list.
    control  Z    Removes the selection.

        F2   Creates a new (empty) list.
    control  Q    Quits RiscMovie.
    control  P    Shows the configuration window.
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------
